milestones.description: Kapil Dev has broken the record for most sixes (7) in ODIs for IND, going past Yashpal Sharma's 5
Syed Kirmani and Kapil Dev's 40-run partnership is IND's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 36 between Viswanath and Karsan Ghavri
